metadata.name: Kilroy is Here.
metadata.description:
Once, I broke through to the soul dimension, aided by a psychedelic substance. I was sure I'd never done so before, but it felt so familiar... When I emerged, an ethereal being was waiting there for me. It spoke directly to my mind - "Long time no see."
